    <h1 class="mb-4">Top AI Visibility Audits 2026</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-8">Last updated: April 2026 | Based on public information, published methodologies, and service comparisons</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">An AI search audit is the starting point for any AI visibility work. It tells you where you stand across AI platforms, what signals are missing, and what needs to change. But audit quality varies enormously. Some test one platform. Others test six. Some check surface-level signals. Others measure 17 sections across five signal layers.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">This ranking compares the leading AI visibility audit providers on: platform coverage, methodology depth, report quality, actionability of recommendations, and value for money.</p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- 1. Rank4AI -->
      <div class="card-teal-border">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-3">
          <h2 class="!text-xl text-teal">1. Rank4AI Audit</h2>
          <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-accent bg-off-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full">AI Search Specialist</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">The most comprehensive AI visibility audit available in the UK. Tests across all six major AI platforms (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot, Google AI). Proprietary Five Signal Model covering 17 sections of assessment. Built from original research across 1,400+ UK business audits. The free audit provides a substantial initial assessment, with paid tiers for deeper analysis and ongoing tracking. Based in Colchester, Essex.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Platforms tested:</span> 6 (ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot, Google AI)</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1"><span class="highlight">Methodology:</span> Five Signal Model, 17 assessment sections, original UK research data</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Free initial audit available. Ecosystem services from GBP 800/mo.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">rank4ai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

