        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-3">Productised audit approach with two tiers: Snapshot Audit for a quick overview and Advanced Audit for deeper analysis. Proprietary "6 Pillars" framework. Dashboard product provides ongoing monitoring after the initial audit, giving businesses a continuous view of their AI visibility rather than a one-off snapshot. SaaS-style pricing makes it accessible.</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Audit tiers:</span> Snapshot Audit, Advanced Audit, Ongoing Monitoring</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1"><span class="highlight">Methodology:</span> 6 Pillars framework with dashboard monitoring</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1"><span class="highlight">Pricing:</span> Monitoring from GBP 100/mo</p>
        <p class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-1">awarenessai.co.uk</p>
      </div>

